result:
.az-search-items
    padding: 0 15px 0 15px
    .v-input__slot
        &:before
            border-color: #ccc !important

    .az-text
        margin-bottom: 8px
        label
            color: #777 !important
            font-weight: bold
            font-size: 13px
        p
            color: #888 !important
            font-size: 13px

    .v-text-field
        .v-label
            color: #777 !important
            font-weight: bold
            font-size: 13px
            overflow: unset

        input:-webkit-autofill
            background-color: white !important

        input
            font-size: 13px
            color: #888 !important

        .v-label--active
            -webkit-transform: translateY(-18px)
            transform: translateY(-18px)

    .v-select__selection--comma
        font-size: 13px
        color: #888 !important

    .checkbox-label
        font-size: 13px
        font-weight: bold
        color: #777 !important

    .v-input__icon i
        font-size: 18px

    .az-checkbox
        i
            font-size: 14px
            margin-bottom: 3px

        .v-input--selection-controls__ripple
            cursor: pointer
            height: 20px
            width: 20px
            left: -1px
            top: calc(50% - 10px)

        .v-input--selection-controls__input
            margin-right: 0
            width: 18px

        .accent--text
            color: #777 !important

        .v-input
            margin-top 0 !important
            padding: 0
            .v-label
                font-size: 13px
                color: #888 !important

            .accent--text
                label
                    font-size: 13px
                    color: #888 !important

    .v-textarea textarea
        font-size: 13px
        color: #888 !important
